title: Silverfish
description: A close-up image of a silverfish, a small, wingless insect with a slender, elongated body and long antennae. The insect has a grayish-brown color and is characterized by its fish-like movements.

title: Scorpion on Green Leaf
description: A close-up image of a black scorpion positioned on a vibrant green leaf. The scorpion is detailed, showcasing its pincers and segmented tail, which is raised.

title: Tarantula
description: A close-up image of a tarantula, showcasing its hairy body and long legs. The spider has a dark brown and orange coloration, with prominent fangs and a robust build.

title: Centipede on Forest Floor
description: A centipede with a reddish-brown body and orange legs is crawling over a bed of dried leaves and twigs on the forest floor.
